{"_path":"/travel/v016","_dir":"travel","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"杭州-旅遊規劃","description":"杭州旅遊-旅遊規劃","image":null,"sequence":16,"category":"6.杭州旅遊","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"旅行導遊"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-28T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"杭州旅遊-旅遊規劃"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"杭州旅遊-旅遊規劃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"旅遊主題-鑑賞古代到現今的杭州"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旅遊主題: 鑑賞古代到現今的杭州"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"杭州有著 2200 年的悠久歷史，是我國八大古都之一，其盛名又以西湖為首，她擁有三面雲山，一水抱城的山光水色，以“淡妝濃抹總相宜”的自然風光傳承至今，情系天下眾生。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南宋時期，杭州曾是南宋王朝的都城。 大運河貫穿中國南北，杭州段是其重要組成部分。運河沿岸的古建築、碼頭等，見證了杭州作為水運樞紐的繁榮。 杭州的歷史不僅僅是建築，更是深厚的文化底蘊。從西湖的詩意到錢塘江的壯觀，從南宋皇城的繁華到運河的悠長，每一處都訴說著一個故事。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"本次旅遊將欣賞江南神韻於一身的西湖十景, 享受自古就有“上有天堂，下有蘇杭”美譽的傳統美食、採購絲綢之府的絲綢、鑑賞文物之邦的歷史古跡。 此外還需見證錢江新城的現代化杭州。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v016-01.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v016-01.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v016-02.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v016-02.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v016-03.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v016-03.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"旅遊證件"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旅遊證件"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"台灣護照"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":